Two British police officers were assaulted with a sword while trying to arrest a man outside Buckingham Palace. (Reuters)At least 7 people are killed and 15 injured after gunmen fire upon a pilgrimage bus and a police vehicle, on the 11th day of the Amarnath Yatra pilgrimage in the Indian city of Anantnag. The attack is believed to be terror-related. (NDTV)(The Indian Express)